   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="inscription" xml:lang="en" decls="#f_E #c_2 #m_I #t_P">
            <ab>HERE LIETH THE BODY OF</ab>
            <ab>HENRY SAPTE. ESQUIRE. OF SOUTHAMPTON.</ab>
            <ab>LATE A CAPTAIN IN THE SEVENTEENTH</ab>
            <ab>BRITISH REGIMENT OF FOOT.</ab>
            <ab>WHO DIED IN THIS CITY ON THE TWENTY SECOND DAY</ab>
            <ab>OF OCTOBER MDCCCXVI.</ab>
            <ab>IN THE FORTY SECOND YEAR OF HIS AGE.</ab>
            <ab/>
            <ab>HIS AFFLICTED WIDOW. WHO ACCOMPANIED HIM TO ROME</ab>
            <ab>CAUSED THIS MONUMENT TO BE ERECTED TO HIS MEMORY</ab>
         </div>
      </body>
